TITLE PlaneNonCompensationInvariants2026v1
ALNSPECHASHHEX 0x????????????????        # fill via hex-stamping
SCHEMANAME ecosafety.plane.noncomp.invariants.2026v1
CATEGORY ECOSAFETY
DESCRIPTION Non-compensation invariants for non-offsettable planes (carbon, biodiversity) under KER.

PARTICLE PlaneNonCompensationInvariants2026v1
  ROLE       INVARIANT
  VERSIONTAG v1
  LYAPCHANNEL governance

  FIELD invariant_id STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Invariant identifier.

  FIELD plane_id      STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Plane identifier, e.g., carbon, biodiversity.

  FIELD nonoffsettable BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION TRUE if this plane is treated as non-offsettable.

  FIELD r_soft        F64   RISKCOORD
    DESCRIPTION Soft threshold for this plane above which non-compensation is enforced.

  FIELD apply_lanes   STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Comma-separated lanes where this invariant applies, e.g., "EXPPROD,PROD".

  FIELD require_K_non_increase BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, K_next must be <= K_prev when triggered.

  FIELD require_E_non_increase BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, E_next must be <= E_prev when triggered.

  FIELD require_R_non_decrease BOOL META
    DESCRIPTION If TRUE, R_next must be >= R_prev when triggered.

  FIELD ownerdid     STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Bostrom DID owning this invariant spec.

  FIELD evidencehex  STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Hex-encoded evidence chain for this invariant definition.

  FIELD signinghex   STRING META
    DESCRIPTION Hex-encoded signature bound to ownerdid.

  FIELD issued_utc   DATETIME META
    DESCRIPTION Timestamp when this invariant was issued.

ENDPARTICLE
